{"tid":884116,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"R.I.P.！巴甲球員被閹割慘死","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:51:04.000Z","uid":87072,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5d7a02c685e3531e9e45045934fb47a6204091","tid":884116,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/272/23418900272/23422405319_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F272%2F23418900272%2F23422405319_600x399.jpg&h=dc80fb01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=2e7d01c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】由聖保羅外借聖賓圖的中場丹尼爾哥利亞，被發現於木叢中被斬首，生殖器官更被砍掉，終年24歲。<br />\n<br />\n周二聖保羅中場丹尼爾哥利亞（Daniel Correa）被發現死在灌木叢中，他的生殖器更被切下。警方指出，24歲的丹尼爾哥利亞在「非常暴力情況下」被殺害。<br />\n<br />\n巴西報章指死因被列為「被刀傷」，據當地傳媒報道，丹尼爾哥利亞遭受酷刑。1名警官說：「自從身體出現以來，顯示是個非常暴力的案件。這名男子脖子上有兩處被深深切傷，他的頭部幾乎被斬首，他的生殖器被割斷了。」<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅球會亦發表聲明，向這名將於今年12月約滿的球員發表深切遺憾：「球會十分同情，並向球員家人表示哀悼。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 球會官網圖片"},{"pid":"c5e759325ceaa661072c8e41226622014dbd42c3","tid":884116,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"鬼國"},{"pid":"b6519c37d7b6455b6fd8e370a45b026df27c14e0","tid":884116,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a636ac15619584079b8d9453df293c9f2be1d8","tid":884116,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"金磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03b8ec27083c89a525922229b65bc51129932ba","tid":884116,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor